---
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
import Button from "@/components/fundations/elements/Button.astro";

---

<section>
  <Wrapper variant="paddingLess">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
      <video
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        class="object-cover object-center w-full h-[60dvh] lg:h-[72dvh] bg-base-50"
      >
        <source src="/services/bgvideo2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <div
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none bg-accent-950/70"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-end gap-y-4">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="displayXL"
        class="text-accent-800 font-display text-balance lg:col-span-2"
      >
AI Readiness Audit: Honest Assessment Before You Waste Money
      </Text>
      <Text
        tag="p"
        variant="textSM"
        class="text-base-600 leading-relaxed"
      >
60% of businesses that buy AI tools aren't ready to use them. Find out if you're in the 40% that are—before you invest. <br /><br />
Most businesses jump straight to buying AI platforms. They see impressive demos. They approve the budget. Six months later? 28% adoption rate and $80K wasted.
<br/><br/>
The problem isn't the AI. It's readiness.

      </Text>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-col lg:flex-row mt-4">
            <Button variant="default" size="xs" class="w-full lg:w-fit">
              Schedule Consultation
            </Button>
          </div>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
  
</section>
